title: 2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 08)

POP: Danny Gokey, Francesca Battistelli, Kari Jobe, Shawn McDonald.  BLUES: Darrell Mansfield, Joe Louis Walker.  ROCK: Farewell Flight, The Fray, Veridia.  INDIE: James Vincent McMorrow, Sandy Harless.  CONTEMPORARY: Jeremy Noland.  FOLK: Key Of David.  Gospel: WoW Gospel.
